text_blocks.content: The documentary evidence would establish that Ms. Maxwell did not travel as alleged in the Indictment; did not conspire with Mr. Epstein, as alleged in the Indictment, and was not present with either Mr. Epstein or any Accuser for significant periods of time between 1994 and 1997. Business records associated with the property identified in the Indictment would detail various employees who worked at the properties during the relevant times. These individuals, were they to be located, would corroborate that they did not observe Ms. Maxwell behaving in any of the behavior alleged in the Indictment.
